Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:43.92,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:45.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It feels familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:50.21,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yes! This atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:52.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This feeling of pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.77,0:01:55.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I've felt it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:58.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.35,0:02:01.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's the old Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,that I see in Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.61,Sai,,0,0,0,,I... finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.24,Sai,,0,0,0,,God has...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:16.32,Sai,,0,0,0,,given me a thousand years...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:21.08,Sai,,0,0,0,,just to show Hikaru this match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:26.79,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(345,115)}The Fifty-Seventh Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:26.79,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Let Me Play Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.16,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:41.81,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:47.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:49.65,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The wind feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that only the people playing the\Ngame can see some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:16.26,Background,,0,0,0,,Well, being where I was during\Nthat game it felt as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see what you were thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I could see what Master Touya was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt as if I was in the very\Nmiddle of that match today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Touya must be really\Ndisappointed, losing to Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:39.14,Memory,,0,0,0,,If I lose this match, I will retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he really mean that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:46.36,Background,,0,0,0,,Ah, that was close.
