Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here first thing in the morning, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't really be serious, can he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone with five titles can't just retire... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:31.37,Sai,,0,0,0,,Y-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Were you thinking about something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Why am I always the one that has to worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:49.64,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\1c&H534439&\bord0\shad0\fscy160\frz7\pos(308,95)\frx4\fry1}Touya Kouyou-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, who were you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya's mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,U-umm... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Shindou-kun, he just became a pro this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember? We played once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes! I remember seeing you on Weekly Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the same age as Akira-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Akiko... I'm sorry, but could you\Nleave the room for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.64,Background,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, you resigned yesterday, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't retire... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that you'd retire if you\Nlost to Sai on impulse, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:06.97,Background,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:11.06,Background,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to make sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! It's not me! Why do you think I'm Sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He reminded me of you during the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of the feeling I got when we played\Nin the Room of Deep Contemplation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't pursue it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who Sai is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:06:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me play Sai again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if it's on the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.75,Background,,0,0,0,,I won't ask him to tell me who he is anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:22.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:26.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:31.22,Thinking,,0,0,0,,We could do that if he plans to\Ncontinue to play on the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:32.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:37.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Master Touya would probably keep\Nit secret from anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.23,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can probably let Sai play from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:44.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He would probably like that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.77,Sai,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.24,Sai,,0,0,0,,I probably don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:56.06,Sai,,0,0,0,,have enough time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:57.91,Sai,,0,0,0,,I can feel it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:00.33,Sai,,0,0,0,,Inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:04.28,Sai,,0,0,0,,The sands of time that were frozen within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:08.76,Sai,,0,0,0,,are mercilessly and without doubt...\Nstarting to flow once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:16.81,Background,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... if I let you play him again, will you\Ntake back what you said about retiring?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't take back what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to retire after the upcoming\Nfifth game of the Jyudan match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just asked you not to do\Nanything crazy like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Retiring is not a great concern for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it might be for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be freed from the constraints and\Nresponsibilities that come from being a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:53.43,Background,,0,0,0,,I won't have to accept any boring interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I won't be able to play Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have this existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:05.65,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The happiness of existing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can play an all absorbing game\Nof Go outside of the title matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The match I played yesterday proves it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can play a game at that high of a level\Nwith someone I've never met before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me play Sai again, Shindou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:46.90,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I have no idea who Sai is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.44,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:52.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There is someone connected to Sai nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Is it Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.85,Thinking,,0,0,0,,or is it one of the other people that visited him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:12.34,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the person who heard that\Nthe Meijin plays go on the Internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,and arranged the match...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:17.17,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.72,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Master Touya should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:29.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:32.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Is it Shindou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't hear what they're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.04,Background,,0,0,0,,That may be okay for you, Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:47.57,Background,,0,0,0,,but not for me! I can't have\Nthat. It'll all be my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.75,Background,,0,0,0,,You want to play Sai again don't you, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai feels the same way! So please\Ngive up on that idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.01,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oga...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you said!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do know who Sai is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! No! I don't know him! I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:18.70,Background,,0,0,0,,Ogata-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you arrange the match between\NSai and the Master!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know who Sai is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me play him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ogata...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Ogata...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Sai, don't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.55,Background,,0,0,0,,If you know him then let me play him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know him! I don't know him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... happened to be watching the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:28.89,Background,,0,0,0,,between Sai and Master Touya on the Internet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogata-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou was visiting the Master in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran away when I went in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard some of what they were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chances are, Shindou and Sai know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He was denying it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all we have to do is ask the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,They know each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.37,Thinking,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou and Sai are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.88,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Shindou and Sai are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogata-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Shindou, wasn't it, who arranged\Nyour match against Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:14:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai challenged me to a game on the Internet\Nfirst thing in the morning yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:08.80,Background,,0,0,0,,Seems like you both watched the match yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:13.02,Background,,0,0,0,,It was a game deserving of my name, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:14.94,Background,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Sai went above me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-kun, ask him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to find out who Sai is as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If Father says that he doesn't know who Sai is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no point in asking him about it any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:46.41,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Ogata-san thinks that Sai and\NShindou are different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:48.87,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I don't have an answer for it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:52.87,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But the one thing I know for certain is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:58.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,that Shindou holds the answer to all of these mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do if both\NShindou and the Master deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Akira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogata-san, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:23.65,Background,,0,0,0,,Did Shindou-kun leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like Mr. Ogata heard me talking about Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Touya came in, too, to top it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he still thinks that I'm Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure Master Touya\Nwon't tell them anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I can let you play the Meijin again, Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong Sai, you look sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that I can let you play him again some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that Master Touya won't\Ntell anyone about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can let you play from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:38.72,Sai,,0,0,0,,From time to time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:42.65,Sai,,0,0,0,,How distant that sounds to me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I just let you play yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. You're always asking for more. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think we'll be\Nable to play him for a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,because there will be a commotion over his retiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be impatient, we've got plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:31.82,Sai,,0,0,0,,There is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:34.42,Sai,,0,0,0,,no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.12,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru may have it but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.83,Sai,,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.84,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\1c&H587D87&\bord0\shad0\fscy120\frz350\move(512,291,512,495)}Japanese Go Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya, is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The game that Kouyou played on the Internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I was watching this game from start to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an awesome match! It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Black Master Touya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But really... I can't see him using computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that computers weren't for either of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:22.96,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shindou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai came back to the Internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going over a game he played\Nagainst Touya Meijin right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it too, Waya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? You saw it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So the opponent, playing White, is Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I told you about him before, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you there was someone\Nreally strong on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:00.12,Background,,0,0,0,,And then Sai... White went here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:04.16,Background,,0,0,0,,What an astounding move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, it went like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:11.59,Background,,0,0,0,,and Black resigned here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:13.42,Background,,0,0,0,,Game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.13,Background,,0,0,0,,Resigned!? Here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a half moku match...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,White's winning? Isn't there\Nanything Black can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he doesn't respond here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's definitely Sente.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,White can't lose any more territory...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.73,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to get a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Black would've gained territory if he had played\Nin the corner instead of connecting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:46.87,Background,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.63,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Black is ahead by a bit this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll need to move there once all\Nthe outside liberties are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't move back there at this point either...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.58,Background,,0,0,0,,But you always miss stuff like this, Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.40,Background,,0,0,0,,Waya, stop making light of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.56,Background,,0,0,0,,This move decided the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:13.15,Background,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&00&\t(1017,2269,1,\alpha&20&)}Shindou-kun, have you calculated it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:16.78,Background,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&30&\t(1475,3227,1,\alpha&80&)}Oh! You noticed it because you usually\Ndon't calculate stuff out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:18.16,Background,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&85&\4a&85&\t(613,1114,1,\alpha&99&\4a&99&)}What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:26.41,Sai,,0,0,0,,Everyone is starting to notice\Nthe strength Hikaru has...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.88,0:20:28.92,Sai,,0,0,0,,I can see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:32.21,Sai,,0,0,0,,The brilliant future that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:36.63,Sai,,0,0,0,,shinning about Hikaru... the future that I lack.
